@@TJvThreadTimer.Active
Description:
Set this property to true to activate the timer. Set this property to false to stop the timer.

================================================================
@@TJvThreadTimer.Delay
Description:
Delay determines how frequently the OnTimer event occurs. Each time the specified delay passes, the OnTimer event occurs.

================================================================
@@TJvThreadTimer.OnTimer
Description:
Occurs when a specified amount of time, determined by the Delay property, has passed.

